findings.title: Incompatibility with Deflationary Tokens
findings.description: The MasterMilker contract's deposit() and withdraw() functions use safeTransferFrom() to transfer assets, which may cause inconsistencies with deflationary tokens' balances.

findings.title: Issue with `deposit()` and `withdraw()` routines
findings.description: Incompatibility issue with deflationary tokens in deposit() and withdraw() functions of CreamyToken contract.
